msgstr "Activado"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1226
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Desactivado"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1232
msgid ""
"Forced ON by the AGNOSIS_DEBUG constant in wp-config.php — the checkbox "
"above has no effect until that line is removed."
msgstr ""
"Forzado a ACTIVADO por la constante AGNOSIS_DEBUG en wp-config.php: la "
"casilla de arriba no tendrá efecto hasta que se elimine esa línea."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1234
msgid ""
"Forced OFF by the AGNOSIS_DEBUG constant in wp-config.php — the checkbox "
"above has no effect until that line is removed."
msgstr ""
"Forzado a DESACTIVADO por la constante AGNOSIS_DEBUG en wp-config.php: la "
"casilla de arriba no tendrá efecto hasta que se elimine esa línea."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1242
msgid "Directory"
msgstr "Directorio"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1245
msgid "Filter with agnosis_debug_dir to redirect debug output elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Filtra con agnosis_debug_dir para redirigir la salida de depuración a otra "
"ubicación."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1252
msgid ".txt file(s) in the directory"
msgstr "archivo(s) .txt en el directorio"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1258
msgid ""
"Delete all .txt files in the debug directory? The directory itself stays in "
"place so future debug writes still land cleanly."
msgstr ""
"¿Eliminar todos los archivos .txt del directorio de depuración? El propio "
"directorio se mantiene en su sitio, de modo que las futuras escrituras de "
"depuración sigan guardándose correctamente."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1263
msgid "Clear Debug Files"
msgstr "Borrar archivos de depuración"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1294
msgid "Term Translation Cache"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1298
msgid "Cached translations"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1301
msgid ""
"AI-translated tag/medium term names, cached so the same term always gets the "
"same translated label instead of a fresh AI phrasing per post. Renaming a "
"term already clears its own cached entry automatically; use the button below "
"only if a cached translation itself is wrong."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1307
msgid ""
"Clear every cached term translation? Nothing is deleted from your site — "
"terms will simply be re-translated by AI the next time they're needed."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1312
msgid "Clear Term Translation Cache"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1344
msgid "Pipeline Logs"
msgstr "Registros del pipeline"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1349
msgid "Clear all log entries?"
msgstr "¿Borrar todas las entradas del registro?"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1350
msgid "Clear All"
msgstr "Borrar todo"

#. translators: %d: total log entry count
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1359
#, php-format
msgid ""
"%d entries total. Logs are pruned automatically according to the Inbox "
"retention setting."
msgstr ""
"%d entradas en total. Los registros se podan automáticamente según la "
"configuración de retención de la bandeja de entrada."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1366
msgid "No log entries yet."
msgstr "Aún no hay entradas de registro."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1371
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Hora"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1372
msgid "Level"
msgstr "Nivel"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1373
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Contexto"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1374
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Mensaje"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1444
msgid "Inbox Tools"
msgstr "Herramientas de la bandeja de entrada"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1448
msgid "Test connection"
msgstr "Probar conexión"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1453
msgid "Test IMAP Connection"
msgstr "Probar conexión IMAP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1455
msgid ""
"Connects to the configured mailbox and reports the total and unseen message "
"count."
msgstr ""
"Se conecta al buzón configurado e informa del recuento total de mensajes y "
"de mensajes no leídos."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1459
msgid "Poll inbox now"
msgstr "Consultar la bandeja de entrada ahora"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1464
msgid "Poll Inbox Now"
msgstr "Consultar la bandeja de entrada ahora"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1466
msgid ""
"Fetches unseen messages immediately without waiting for WP-Cron. Then click "
"\"Process Pending Queue\" to run the AI pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Obtiene inmediatamente los mensajes no leídos sin esperar a WP-Cron. "
"Después, haz clic en \"Procesar cola pendiente\" para ejecutar el pipeline "
"de IA."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1470
msgid "Process queue"
msgstr "Procesar cola"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1475
msgid "Process Pending Queue"
msgstr "Procesar cola pendiente"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1477
msgid ""
"Immediately runs the AI pipeline on all pending queue items without waiting "
"for WP-Cron. Use this to test the end-to-end flow after a poll."
msgstr ""
"Ejecuta inmediatamente el pipeline de IA sobre todos los elementos "
"pendientes de la cola sin esperar a WP-Cron. Úsalo para probar el flujo "
"completo tras una consulta."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1481
msgid "Force reprocess"
msgstr "Forzar reprocesado"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1486
msgid "Force Reprocess Inbox"
msgstr "Forzar reprocesado de la bandeja de entrada"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1488
msgid ""
"Resets failed/stuck/orphaned queue rows back to pending, then immediately "
"polls for unprocessed messages. Then click \"Process Pending Queue\" to run "
"the AI pipeline. Already-published artworks with valid posts are never re-"
"processed."
msgstr ""
"Restablece las filas de cola fallidas, atascadas o huérfanas a pendiente y, "
"a continuación, consulta inmediatamente los mensajes sin procesar. Después, "
"haz clic en \"Procesar cola pendiente\" para ejecutar la canalización de IA. "
"Las obras ya publicadas con entradas válidas nunca se reprocesan."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1522
msgid "Pending Applications"
msgstr "Solicitudes pendientes"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1525
msgid "No pending applications."
msgstr "No hay solicitudes pendientes."

#. translators: %d: number of positive votes currently required for admission
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1531
#, php-format
